Punj Lloyd Gains in Mumbai After Qatar Solar Awards Contract

-- B y   N i v e d i t h a   R a v i
-- 
2011-10-05T03:49:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/punj-lloyd-gains-in-mumbai-after-qatar-solar-awards-contract.html
Punj Lloyd Ltd. (PUNJ)  gained as much as 2.1
percent in Mumbai after Qatar Solar Technologies, a unit of the
 Qatar Foundation , awarded an engineering, procurement and
construction contract to Punj Lloyd Group. The shares rose 1.6
percent to 53.25 rupees at 9:16 a.m. local time.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Niveditha Ravi at 
 nravi2@bloomberg.net  